+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **UNION Injection --- Beyond Login Bypass**                           |
|                                                                       |
| Once an attacker knows injection is possible, they can extract data   |
| from other tables entirely. Try this in the Juice Shop product        |
| search:                                                               |
|                                                                       |
| > %\' UNION SELECT id, username, password, role, email FROM Users\--  |
|                                                                       |
| The UNION keyword appends a second SELECT. The injected SELECT        |
| fetches from the Users table, not the Products table. The results     |
| appear in the search results.                                         |
|                                                                       |
| **Column count must match:** the injected SELECT must return the same |
| number of columns as the original query. Discovering the column count |
| is the first step in a UNION attack --- try adding NULL values one at |
| a time until the error disappears.                                    |
