  ----------------- ----------------- ----------------- -----------------
  **Colour Key**                                        

  **■ Dark blue**   **■ Green** ---   **■ Red** ---     **■ Purple** ---
  --- fixed SQL     legitimate user   injected syntax   parameterised
  template          input             characters        placeholder
                                                        (safe)
  ----------------- ----------------- ----------------- -----------------

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **The root cause of ALL injection attacks:** user-supplied data is
  interpreted as code or command structure. The universal fix: **keep
  data and structure separate.** Parameterised queries do this for SQL.
  The same principle --- never concatenate user input into commands ---
  applies to every injection type on this course.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
